CHALUKYA RAILWAY INSTITUTE, SOUTH WESTERN RAILWAY, HUBLI

CHALUKYA RAILWAY INSTITUTE

SOUTH WESTERN RAILWAY

GADAG ROAD , HUBLI

Facilities available :

Auditorium with built in Stage, Green Rooms & Family suits.

Separate Dining Hall with Kitchen facilities and Spacious Parking area.

MUTI PURPOPSE SPORTS COMPLEX

Indoor Games: Billiards , Table- tennis , Carom Boards,

Chess Boards etc.

Out Door : Shuttle Badminton , Volleyball etc.

A well equipped Library and Reading Room with English, Kannada & Hindi News Papers & Periodicals.

For Auditorium Tariff: Contact Chalukya Office.
